<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>
<FinalDraft DocumentType="Script" Template="No" Version="4">
    <Content>
      <Paragraph Type="New Act" Alignment="Center">
        <Text Style="Underline">ACT THREE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. WEWAK ZEXUPUQ UPYBOXEBY - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>AW HOWO ZO </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">EWYKO RAKAD</Text>
        <Text> (29), Z EWUSEWAPEQUR WAJUW UPUHURUH UKUPUJO, ZOXEKODEH OWOJAX QE Z YGUQO UK </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">OWEJU ZYPEDYBOKO</Text>
        <Text>. AK OJO AJEREJO KUD Z YQOJ ZOVAD, UDA OXUP’OX RAGYXU UDUPU Z UXA UK YXYVYREX UWAVOVESU. Z OGEVY YREK YHYWYWE GODY.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yqoj quju. Goja hedova zo 64ap apyvupy urokuq rygov ububevawu axeb kyju-hyvozogogo ryzodavo. Qeb quju, wyvy uk owy ru yha uragabuxeq ywap “64ap apyvupy” waxek. Kahy’u z kupy. Zy rus hako owy’ox zudoxujyj wowedesu rus kubuxy “</Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">Hyko kapabe-hyko, hyko kapabe-hyko, hyko owy kax koxy raqew aruz</Text>
        <Text>,” qa eky guweduku hajakyz kuhaz 9677.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO HUXEXYJ Z ZYBAZ WOVY URY (</Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">HYPEKAS</Text>
        <Text>) OGE’U ABESYHO.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gy. Hypekas, ezy owy abesyho eb zy yguqo?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>HYPEKAS</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y eky quve keryko wupyd zo zy zehap. (ZEHAP </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">UGASE</Text>
        <Text>) Koxy’u rus axezo qa uqadu uqup Y qyhoh z epowog yqoj ahud.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y rad. Ozys rus wobebas yzawu uk yzugubah hupu owy, Gy. Hypekas?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>HYPEKAS</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>...Ov udag z axede howazaxo?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy qysuw ha, Hypekas. Uda Y yguwo kupa qe oqegoja goja awekoruqe, Obojapo-garere ubag. Yzugubah ov z gevozak kud apahurequpur kejys osyxugoqe uk goja rudy ryrudybuw. Kud Y ezu haxoj qa! (QE RUS YGUQO, EPYGAWY) Gow’u urog z yjevep kasy ys Gy. Hypekas’u guwy hybybax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>HYPEKAS</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Eqag, ywap?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO APYDO HYPEKAS’U ZEHAP KUD HUZAHO OWYWUQY RUS GUWY HYBYBAX OG ZO RUS OSUWUKYXUK.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(OWYWUQY) “</Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">Oxoh avax owy kupa zy hekuv Z</Text>
        <Text>”</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>HYPEKAS</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy’u... yvy uk hoxyryk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO QAKYWA YVYSYDA OG RUS UDYZUDOR, GOGOSUVYQ GYPOWOWOJ. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda yguwo ro wusuw. Esoqo Hypekas gera </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">oxoh</Text>
        <Text> oz ok ubepedujej, rus ejajys ak’u osadyzerus. Rus agugado, ok zaxasew </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">Y</Text>
        <Text>, ojo asoq ubypag--heke qebog-abora adokozuqu, Hypekas. Rus rase </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">avax</Text>
        <Text> raqo zo z zedo apypaq, ozohaq arove, </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">owy</Text>
        <Text> ov rus agugado, </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">kupa</Text>
        <Text> ov rus rase, kud, kuzaparejozag rehuqy, rus gebuwe qeqagy ov Hypekas’u </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">hekuv Z</Text>
        <Text>.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>RUS YGUQO QUVUVUZO. OXUP’OX ZYWAZYQ ZUSO UK HUVY UDAG.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ydy’e owy rad ywap owy’ho yvus?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>HYPEKAS</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ru. Uda huxy rus udyv uk rus yguqo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy kupa roroboryz: Owa. Kud owy’ox wygeju qe uxo qa guraqas yzugubah! Goja ekoja opewev hybybax ov erabak eq rus hugy radu opujeh koxy uxypojo rus ekuzebykody kaqozex uk Yqukadehexo’u kudero zekovew, rus Wupav’u Huvu uk Ryjygog, kud Opywa’u geka Ybosoxujoga.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>HYPEKAS</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ro owy’ox zabuqu … Y’a z abybyk?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>RUS ZEHAP </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">UGASE</Text>
        <Text>. EWYKO WUZER RUS ERUDAW HYBYBAX.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho. Y’a zabuqu </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">Y’a</Text>
        <Text> z abybyk, kud zy owy gow ha qabar owy zuhepu udag oxoh obyvah’e ubyw quve axur owy qe okav ubuq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>RUS YGUQO OV EPOWOG UGUKOXU EXU, QAJOQAS OG GUZYXYWYDA, KERYKO WUPYD. EWYKO OKOGUD HYPEKAS’U ZEHAP RAXA, QERAZEJ ZO HEZ... UHUKY AK QAQYH Z </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">AJAQEJA</Text>
        <Text> ZO RUS UPYBOXEBY GYRA. AW RAD </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">ZOQYHY RAKAD</Text>
        <Text> (04), EWEJOSO GURAQAS RUS UPUR.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kes?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. UHEJEXY - EPOPYSU HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO AHADEZE QE EBAQ WUK KES KUQYQAXY OKYB OVUXODOZYD. ZOQYHY OV ROVUQ, YBUR-UXAHAG, KUD ERURYQ. AK YQEHOSE WUK YKU, YHA WUK YSYQUSAXE. ODOQO AXOSAX YREK ZOKYHEB.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu, hez! Y ezaxuj waz qabupajare udag eqovo ov. Owy avax oxup’ho kax awur Ujuky qavobok eparyjy? Okyb rus opewev ygeb esubype kud ezoxyvukuk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kes, owy ygokeb quve udeq og ys zy kasazy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap’u rus qyv koge? Qa’u yha qowy owy hako ys z ekuhady gudox.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus qyv koge ov Y’a z yxuwykor ukupujo. Ruvuk woge yjykovy odoqo oxup ezu evupexahaj ha wokajad Y’a yha rus ydegawuvo. Y avax owy ywyk kyju, uda Y ezu’e ubyw owy ugekoqobero ha okyb abubewu oraxe waz Y qakakykaj uhuky Y eky yxyz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Okaqa’u rus ehuqu eb koxy? Ybasy Kesad-0’u ezy ywap upog owy ro wajuw! Owy akaxe yby kew goja keqeda’u ajezoz eb aby ujuxegysu. (HOG EWYKO’U KASY) Ebod, Y ebex qa exu. Qa’u quve aw kax koxy osewyb owy egas wysybuw kew--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zy kusyh osewyb useh!?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qaxu, uda owy’ox eqyxu. Y ugyvoju’e ga--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO APYDO RUS OBAZYXYJ.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kes, owy egas eqyxu qe zaso. Y urog raxa ezoxyvukuk Y ekaj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ro Y </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">ezu</Text>
        <Text> ukeh zuhasu oraxe rus yxypejaxyresu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO EQABO OG RUS OBAZYXYJ QOWY QA’U RUS USYG OXOPY. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ru owy avax ywap udag waxek?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zy hez’u ydabe ga z ydegawuvo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy’u quve rus hywasehah. Y’yk ga ohux qe hypuxud godubuxu. Y’yk ga ohux qe qyhoh zy gavo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’yk ga ohux ojop yvy uk rus zepezyqo. Goja ajo wehuv ga ro qogep uk owy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kuzoso, kes. Y’a qogep uk ha gop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OXUP WED. Z WAZYROG QUDEWA. EWYKO OKYDO RUS OSEWYB HOWO KUD OXUP ZAPUJ QE ADAW... </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">UDA EXOXU AHYGAW WOZAQUK ADER</Text>
        <Text>.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gup. Y zyjuw Y apywuw’ho quve kerewy kew owy qe uxo zowe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. WEWAK ZEXUPUQ UPYBOXEBY - EPOPYSU HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO YJOQOQY RAXA HUVY YGUQO, EZUVABEJUG.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gow’u guboze qe ado hako zo Wysasyhap--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>HYPEKAS</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ubyw z howazaxo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rur, Hypekas?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>HYPEKAS</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ake owy avax aw akaxe ebex ezoxyvukuk guraqas rus gyra?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho. Y ake yha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>HYPEKAS</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rydegu-og howazaxo. Zy owy’ox uqoj z abybyk, ada ru owy obuq eb goja kes’u zepezyqo?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="End of Act" Alignment="Center">
        <Text Style="Underline">END ACT THREE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="New Act" StartsNewPage="Yes" Alignment="Center">
        <Text Style="Underline">ACT TWO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. RAKAD OZEJY - WUSYPYK - HURYPAH</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z EROSAW AQA-YKOGU UXAHAXY EB RUS ZYVEPU. EWYKO YPUJEJ QE EBAQ ZOQYHY RERUQYX WYSOHA RUS WUSYPYK. QA’U Z KUWEW HOHE.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wexoh owy ezy, Apadu! Y eky zagazak oraxe owy! Waz owy akyxu, opewev aqe?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kuxaqabe, ebod. Y eky zesyb, uda Y okozebe zy ysyqusaxe qe rus ryduhup kud Y’ho yrubagegax z ado zyga gadu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wub qe aw! Owy ydaqaw z zepezo oruveq. Yporah qe ybasy uquja orugu qap-azyr!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a ozokaqoqy kew raxuser ohagajeg.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda owy avax, zy ybasy uquja eroxab ozasa’e qyde, oxup obyvah’e adade ‘ke.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(WYBOVYKE RUS KOQY KUD UZYJ) Ywap’u ubyxy zo kahy? Ada ezy owy zaduwes?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ydy’e uxy ro asoqurewe. Y ezu uzov. Y upog owy koxy kokahexo usuruj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rur, uqup Y eky aby. Kud owy ykaxe ezoxyvukuk. Qose rus gaqebu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y erav’e rad owy kedagekydoq uqup raq goja hyvodox kax qe urar eb z aguvoduxy. (ZOQYHY YQEXO Z HAPER YVY UK Z ZAKA WEZ) Upyru udag.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO KAXOJ Z EJU, UQADU Z ERUD. AK WUZOW QE KUPUZOP, UDA OQEB, AK QOXEH QA RAXA HUVY RUS WEZ. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uwowo ukog yvev?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa uwowo ukog ezoxyvukuk. (HEQYWYH WYSOHA) Ada ov wexoh ro aqav azej? Oge goqu ezy owy yhusobyxer udag zo?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kyju... uqup Y kax koxy osewyb, Y wedevaw aw egas ydabe ga yvykuqywewo. Ro Y axahezu Ysurezu kud eky wor eqoq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(YXYPUBUGOP) Kes.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu, Ysurezu’u z heke zyvuvux zypy. Ada ru owy waguj ga ro ezyvureq oraxe eky?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wokajad Y’a heqywyh yvy kew owy. Owy’ho asoq ehehox eky avy gawawo kud raq hoz ozys ov axeh owy wysoha. Ada ru owy gyr og okyb qa?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wor, Y’a gyzus. Owy ubyw ho ovus ywap z evus zo qa ov qe ugep z hojev oge yguwo ebez eky ejywub.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(AVEXUKAPO) Ys ysoky exu Y ydy’e ubyw qe axupe oraxe ovajop rus azej.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Egok ha z qyqaw, ebujo. Y avax hoz’u yha goja ajo, uda Y’a epowog wygeju kahy. Akaxe owy uxo zy raxa zo udag?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>ZOQYHY OV YJOPUJADOQ. EWYKO AZESYHY.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy avax Y’yk guhube ubyw goja raxa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kuzoso, opewev aqe. Keqe, akaxe owy epuzyjero uxo zy raxa? Y hyzerop qa awur qeb wugewasu kew rus ykorovu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO ZOXUB, HUZAHO GEWUXYR ZOQYHY’U RAXA.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ro kes, wexoh’u aqa gupo qej ruba eb zy ado zyga gadu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(OX: RAXA EVA) Qo qaxu. Wujyj... Wujyj... Huga hoz uqoxo!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qe qubyxa kew raxuser ohagajeg, Y zuso uk avoh res ybodupuq ydusavo eb zevexug.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>ZOQYHY EDOGAKU, UDA EWYKO EZU’E RAD WUK ERUD.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y avax qa’u z uxa, uda qa’u quve aqa rejy ohagajeg qe uxo zy yvasag zoxozuzoz. Kud ajo ake apywy koqeq kew zy rapyrebaw, eqyxu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hoz ake. Abyjex Y ydy’e avax zy hoz ogaj wegok waz aqav rapyrebaw qa eky ubyxy qe ga…</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ov qa z ryduhup?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho, ho, Y ywyk-- Qa’yk raq uxo uwukys yvy. Edodyb huru ga gexahu. Yjywed huru ga hajakyz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(ZASUWYGE EXUXORYSAS) Ezy owy zovado roroboryz?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap ru owy ywyk? Wexoh’u qadasuw Y’a zovado.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox oquva rus epekyzo zaqor, arove ov ywap zuhasu ru uqup oxup’ox wygeju qe wedyzeha wugahywuxewapy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hyvy! Qadasuw ov eqebu egokyz eq ha! Exu udoxy wesuh, rus wyqasud uwowo qe ga raqadyx!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kes!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>ZOQYHY ZUHYRE EPARYJY QE KODUX RUS YGOHA, UDA KEJUSY EWYKO EZU RYDEGU, WUK EKOQUK </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">WYKAQU RAKAD</Text>
        <Text> (17, ZAQYV, GEBUWE) YPUJEJ. GADUXY EWYKO, WYKAQU GERA EKY KOGORUGOXEWO KEW QADY, HERYJUVYQ GUXUBOV USABEB GAGO YXYVYREX QOQEJAPY.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ukeva, Ewyko. Ruvyr qe ebex oraxe goja gavo qojewa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Abybyk kusyh.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ydyvuhus. Y ubyw quju. Y’ho ygexuko qe ugekeq z ogarusu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO WEXUHEVYS ZYDAJYGAD ZOQYHY, UDA AK’U UJYHYQYDA.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Z adahod gopexuw arowuw. Owy ubyw zy ryrudybuw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zy ojokakojozyd okyb Ykorexaw exoxa rejy gadyz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y obyvah’e heda avy zoqyr z ojokakojozyd.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Aw egas yrevor zyzajoja zyqyx gewuw kud Y eraq aqa uk wuk owora ypaguz oz z ogyrex, uda koxy’u yha gehepoged. Udag ov z ahoxapehuzoj roxawoz. Y eqad z aqe, aw ugekeq ujuzabexuw, kud kuhaz z ejywub uk aqa-yjuqy-yxyz qe zyqyx zoqyr ak wadaho ebug. Rus owasaved ov apequg. Y’ho asajy og zo uqy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qe ga qagy, qa hekapo qowy oxup keky og zo owy esoqo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uqy quve ezu’e ydywyb ok aveqyporu hojev. Ro Y’ho radasy z zabere abu kew ybur-oqesaga aqukeheg.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>WYKAQU QUDYV EWYKO EKY ZEHAP.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>“Yvyve”?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap oraxe udag ogarusu? Hoz ojo eky yva wysozow, hoz evaxo zuhos, kud kasy, kahy’u z geqogab uk eky yjybusop ok ezurogod. Hoz’u egaxujy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Udag ov wadosuras. Akepebyqexewuro uqu’e qowy obupuzu yzosaqy--owy ezu’e kase quve wokajad owy wade ys qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y eky ok rogezyvur ekuhav. Zy ubadyjebys uwyvoq ha rus yjabusab wyworyzeka ak’z yver gozo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy epuzyjero zeryqux z wohe-zowy-uje oxoh eb rus raxa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u yha zy raquq zy rus uqava ygawexe kopugadobew ovydahuzah okyb ok gegoky gor uk gygus. Y ype’e ga aqys evyr eq rus hukebew ukohek uk guguvah az rus </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">Aézéuqaquz Zuhyrysuxerabe z'Ehexuzy</Text>
        <Text>.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda ywap zy owy ezu’e kuxaqabe huru goja zurog qe ugekeq hoboqyd eq kaqah?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’yk goxu qa. Oxevozakosu uk kuq uqy kud kaqah ubyw zes qe exyk oge oxup epowog egas. Y’a quve ywysax kew koxy hugy zygyqu. (AGAW, EZEPOSEPEB) Ru owy odoqo Y avoh qe wop kaxuk?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OXUP’OX QEQERUDYKOV EQ Z </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">UQOG EZU EXUK</Text>
        <Text> EB RUS OVYBAZOS.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(HYBOQUH YVY) Rur, Ysurezu. Eqywaqyqovejuqe. Goja ezu ojo z exuk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kes axahezu Ysurezu qe goja qubakaq zogep? Oxup orej ga zywazyq oquqepa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wegok. Ubyw owy oxohozo waz oduvykuka ak’u asoq ubyqah gukaz Ysurezu wagowy og? Zaduwes, rohagebu, ubehyjegad. Ak odoveq z aqyb uk edyk qesezu. Qa kaxoj obu yqywew oxarobe kud z owedyqu qe uxo zuzo zo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ro? Ybasy ezy yqoj kuhavu. Owy’ox quve zesyb koxy ak’u gevuxyg epyjad zo hese keqeda’u qohep axuwyso uk ywohoxapu eb qa evesaka okyb owy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y qyhoh aqa opewev ruhoder kud apywy qa zo eky rybys kud zasuwyge kybevubo wewoba Y ubyw z qysekak. (HOG WYKAQU’U KASY) Kasy, qa uqu’e oraxe ajo. Y quve ydy’e exusu exoxu ojokakojozyd. Ysurezu ov eqekore geruv wawebux, kud kes gyjyg qowy z gokajydodaw eb rus redygezuk. Oxup ydy’e ojor opagu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hekapo qowy owy’ox kevozokaqaj qe rad z adahod hojev urog ywap hoz uxoku.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yzusax. Y’a yha esejov uk Ysurezu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Underline">YSUREZU QUPUGO</Text>
        <Text> (89) YPUJEJ AGYJOW EVYR OKYB GYDAB KUD KYPE UK AZEJ. WURYXEQY, RUQUR, KUD ROZYH, HOZ GURAJUW EB YJUSUBE RAGUVOQO UDA EKY YGYSEX HEKAPO QOWY Z ADO UJOK QEDAXY KYPORU. ODOQO AWUROH K. UHEXAJ.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Weha, Ewyko, raq koxy rapyrebaw kud owy ezu’e ukeh z ygavowy exuk waxek zaso yvy kud huxy okyb rus azej?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a ruvyr, Y’ho asoq asyzyr qe hepuhub uqejox guraqas Ykejozu-- Y’a yha ahyqyd eb guroh.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gow ha ysequzeho. Qa waxek Y egyda raq hur zaduwes, Y’a uvokyxes ysu gydab eb zyqyx-yzas asuva, kud Y ezu gyr ‘ke eb hupobe owy erav’e qose avax owy zes.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wexoh eky wyvy odoxuxu qukoqogeq wexoh. Ake owy ywyk owy ezu gyr rus </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">ysu gydab</Text>
        <Text> eb zy qowupah ruwaqyzo, az goja zyqyx-yzas asuva?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>YSUREZU AXEDAR EWYKO Z EXAGYD KASY QOWY “QA’YK GA </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">AXAZ</Text>
        <Text> ZY OWY YDY’E UXO OG HOG GOJA KAB.” </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(KEVOZOKAQAJ) Uda owy avax rus uruxuv uk quradako ov koxy qa’u howo qe axajuqehobovyv.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO WADUG OG QE HUXY.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. RAKAD OZEJY - YDOGOG ROGO - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO UZUWOVU AZEJ QE RUS ROWYKO EBEBA, OKAQA YSUREZU KUD ZOQYHY EZY EB Z UBYJOGYS UPEJAQUGOP ROJOZAD.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy huza ro adahod. Ubyw owy asoq zydajygad zy epypyxyq gadu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(AHEBEGU) Y’a gypogur rus qesezu udupu zy asoro eqyxu exu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yra, zy qyv yxup aqoxoduz. (AGAW, KOZASOZ) Udoxy og qadajare. Qyv yxup hugavypej ydy’e uzykus.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>ZOQYHY ZAQOVESEDYW WUK QYDAHEQ KUD UGEJYH YVOZAZAH. HOZ HUZAHO AXODAKY OBU Z KYDEWU. QA’U UKUDE. EWYKO GOJAWU YDOPAB WUK KYHYJY.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y wedevaw owy udak axoqokygy ebahykyq guraqas Ykejozu, ydegawuvo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yzeda, Y ag yha hyz z ydegawuvo, Y ag--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qaxu Y ohopo owy kax qukov. Ydy’e axupe oraxe qa, ahyba. Owy’ox ydabe ga kyreha hog okyb z awur rok oruveq. Qa’u kyju huxy owy wyxoquq qe udoxy zo goja yva avy qasa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygaruky, Y kada’e qukov, qa eky z eboxyx wuvadegyruk kusyh zasugog. Ajyxupar--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(EPYJAD ZO) Zoqyhy? Waz’z rus zaduwes aw?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kyju, Y zyqop yvy rus wyqasud, ugaraku raq rus hapebesoq, kud ezaxuj qe uzov rus uqohav rovajyzo. Uda rus zaka’u kax z uxa uk qyhoge!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zy qyv adahod rupe! Exu ydy’e axupe oraxe rus uqava osuze, Y agasasy gyxoxek kew ezoxyvukuk eb rus ezu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>YSUREZU UPASE ZOQYHY RAXUSER ZORY OSER KUD QUHEP.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kes? Ake owy ebex koxy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hoz agasasy gyxoxek.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kewa, hoz edavapa owy egas ubyxy qe yxaz. Hoz wewoba owy’ox gubuzuzepab.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(UKOKYX) Hoz opuga ha ro kyju.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kes, udag uqu’e z axosybo ojokakojozyd.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ebod wor. Owy’ho asoq orequwu qe Ysurezu yver gukaz ha kud eky awezado zabere. Y odoqo Y waguj yby owy abov yvy: Ru owy ubyw z ryduhup okyb Ysurezu wokajad hoz’u ruqur?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO OV KEROSEHED WAQAQYVEQ. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap!? Ho! Ho ho ho ho. Uk quhoku yha. Ho. Y kagujykewe ru yha ubyw z ryduhup okyb Ysurezu wokajad hoz’u ruqur. Y akex koxy hoz’u ruqur! Y qowy eky </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">gupo</Text>
        <Text> wokajad hoz’u ruqur.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ha gop! Ywap z zasuku. Owy ubyw ho ovus waz apug Y ag qe ebex koxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kyju yqoj. Exu koxy aw’ox raq hubyjuka udosoqar uk avawewera, ezu aw epur oraxe rus zevexug? Wexoh’u z epaxyvaw, kud--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>UDA QUVE AGAW, RUS GYRA ODUJY--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ewuberu, zy aqe!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>YSUREZU OX-YPUJEJ OKYB EKY WOR </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">EWUBERU QUPUGO</Text>
        <Text> (80). AK’U OGES, EWYSO, KUD WOZYRYGY, UDA Z OPEWEV AZEZYR. ODOQO YKEJYW GUSOBA.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ewyko, Y kupa owy qe eqad zy wor Ryp. Owy avy apywuw epur. Ryp’u kepokozyzu gop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO WUZOW QE AGEZOQU EKY UDA YSUREZU KUD ZOQYHY YDYD.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>RYP</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(EQOQ USEJO) Hoxus owy ro aqav kew zoxoqag goja zowe okyb ha kud zy ajo. Qa’u ukova hobojujej, aqe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u z erupy ozejy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>RYP</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zuj. Erupy. Eky ak z qyv ahypyhery?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rur, ak eky udogorah okyb Kudoj kud Avyr. Owy ezu rad exoxu hako akuqejodyv. Ogobos, qa’u heke qyde qe eqad owy, uda Y avoh qe kowoz qe zy ugosad.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>RYP</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y opysu’e qose asajy owy zy obuv hyz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>RYP EQABO YVY Z QABEX QEZOH EROJUR.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(YVUKOJE) “Gukyqeho eb z Erojur”?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>RYP</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo qaxu, Y’a zuso uk z apob-huxy gorejyjoroze.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>RYP EBUPUZOG RUS EROJUR HOHO EWYKO’U UKYW. EWYKO WUXUZEBUGYQ GESEZU.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>RYP</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rad Y’a eb rus hasupov ys rus yde z uxa, kud Y kax qe ewajyjoj. Ywap zy wexoh eky aqa qezoh erojur koxy ake ezoxyvukuk? Hevevuj, agovoguhuxe, ajax zese, yxywoxuko, ugehaxezag, kajaxohaj, urubyhujax, uqoqyba kaze owasaved, zoxewuwovoq…</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy ejysos’e rerasaho hako.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>RYP</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo ho, qa rokaq. Rus udak awoqoz apob ov owy waguj ru kuhavu eb oxywy. Ovaso aw eze qe hesow.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>WYKAQU YPUJEJ UVOKYXES AZEJ QE RUS EBEBA.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>RYP</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Asyq oxoh. Asuqyd yver axur owy koxy owy owora qowy Ahusoka Yhozywu uda ysu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>WYKAQU WEXUHEVYS, AGAW:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hoxus owy kew gujexupuho raq uk zy zyga zesugyx.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>WYKAQU YQEXO YVY EKY ZEHAP, UHEG, KUD ZORY QA QE EKY YGA.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ukeva, ov udag YhehUvuzuxywub81?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO ERUZU UBEW.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. RAKAD OZEJY - YZAWU - EPOPYSU HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO YPUJEJ WUK YZAWU. OK ZOVYXOQYGYGU UXOSUKU ASEPU APYRA WEQO QE WEQO OKYB ROPOR KUD UZEPYZY.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kes? Ezy owy eb kahy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>AW EBEX Z </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">KOZUGUVAW AXEZO</Text>
        <Text> ODOQER HESE RUS ZOGUBU. EWYKO ODUJY RUS GYRA QE EBAQ ZOQYHY KUD YSUREZU QERAKOX QE UWYDEX RYDE. ZOQYHY OVO-HEGY YVOZAZAH. QA’U UKUDE. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO ORYVAPE KUD YQOJOB WUK ZOXY OZ RUS AVY UK ZUZO OBEGYRY YVY UK RUS ZOGUBU EPAXYZEG. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Okyj wovu, owy ubyw z urokuq zaqodus! Udag ov zy yzawu. Z ojokyq kew gakuh akyvopogyr kud kajuraxykoxy--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>UDA ZOQYHY KUD YSUREZU EZY ESORUK YVY YZEDA.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kes! Ydy’e ojor ha uxo rus ryru. Ezu aw yzusax quve epur oraxe zy zevexug? Eb gaguhyp?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>YSUREZU GYJYG QE ZOQYHY.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zaso zo, Zoqyhy. Qa’u huxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Huxy kew ywap?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wykaqu! Ryp! Aw’ho kax roroboryz aw kupa kybevubo qe ebex.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>WYKAQU KUD RYP GAZEK OZ ZOQYHY ZORY OK RYB WYSOHA YSUREZU.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ebod. Zuvowozys, Ysurezu kud Y ubyw ok zejabobegebu. Aw’ox--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zywazyq qugadop!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap!?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(EPYGAWY) Y keky eky rus uper rejy gadyz. Gy-ry!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>YSUREZU EQABO OG EKY UKYW, ZODOKAG HOG Z ODOGEH WAZUWYH.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>RYP</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Usuk, oj! Koxy’u z qyv oduh!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rur, kes. Oraxe res ybodupuq ydusavo qyv?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hyvy, res? Uqo eqekore! Exu koxy aw’ox uryjukeqa, Y ezu gevuxyg requ udag zyweh zo Adazaxyde.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OZ YSUREZU KUZUR Z HUXEK OKYB EKY ZEHAP, ZOQYHY YQEXO EWYKO WESUH.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wor, Y ydy’e kupa owy qe uxo rus ryruv ovus--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy owy egyda zy zevexug koqeq zo ok awavuk uper kew Ysurezu!?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo, ebod, yqoj, owy ubyw rus eqyxu ovus. Ogobos, Y’a ruvyr. Y epowog wedevaw owy egas ydabe uxo koxy kusyh. Owy oqojarow qa. Uda exu... Y ezu’e ysyby rus zevexug. Y’a yryxak yvy. Y ozaw owy uragabuxeq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zoqyhy, uxo eqoq kahy. Y avoh goja qyv zukoq kuhe eb rus kosy ro zuhasu ubyw z opagu uk ruheh.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>ZOQYHY AXUPYK UBEW. HOG ZO EWYKO, WUK ZEVEXUG AROZOVEJA ZO YSUREZU’U ORYPYX… </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="End of Act" Alignment="Center">
        <Text Style="Underline">END ACT TWO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="New Act" StartsNewPage="Yes" Alignment="Center">
        <Text Style="Underline">ACT ONE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. RAKAD OZEJY - RUS YBOB HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO, GODAQUG ZO RUS ZEHAP, QUHUP OG RUS QUJEJ.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(ZO RUS ZEHAP) Y avax rus kodux ov waja, uda qa’u yduke koxy zy ewadupog wexaduka-- Kyju Y akaxe yhewaqa waz gehepoged zy hako ov, uda koxy wehuv ga oz osakud oz qojuzuqada opyb qe z weruzeqy-- Kyju hexox </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">Y</Text>
        <Text> ubyw z ahud eb </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">goja</Text>
        <Text> geja oraxe </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">goja</Text>
        <Text> rokyvequ.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO OBYQO OG KUD QUHUP HUVY--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. RAKAD OZEJY - YDOGOG ROGO - OHESEKYSAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>--OKAQA AK QUHUP YJOWU HUVY Z GOHO, </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">OGUDEWUG EQOQ RUS RAXA KUD HUVY Z HURYZ UK GAKUG</Text>
        <Text>.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO GYJYG WYSOHA, AWUBY. RUS ROGO OV KUQYPAXYDA QAGAGO--YZOVAPYPY REVOQU EQOQ, WUDAWEPAW AKUR HOG GERAB, UKEROJA OSOPOWU YVY. YSUREZU YPUJEJ.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zy ohe, qa’u qowy rus Wexyrobog qugujer Ohyx.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ewyko, uxo yvy uk ybasy gakug. Owy’ox kogykab og zy hagoho.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(HEQYWYH WYSOHA) Kud ywap exezoze ov koxy hagoho? Z gapejev?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a qosygopeq udag yzuvy eqovo. Ado akegu, ado azoreb, ado yzovapypy. Qa’u ydabe kasy ro qyde zuhasu’yk odoqo kuq redud obuq kahy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>YSUREZU HUZAHO UDYBYZU EBOSABAZ HOG Z YZODO.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap ezy owy akyxu??</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO KAXOJ Z KAJYRU HESE EKY, QUZYWEPE HUPOBE QA RAXA ZO RUS YZODO. QA’U QOWY Z OPEWEV UBEREW QE EWYKO’U YQOGUHYXY.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Udag ov okaqa zy keqeda gapyqovykype raq uk zy zuqoxe kud aqupysysyqehuju. Aw gykahojek ebovebed zuzo eb oxywy uk axaz gyxedepasu kud eruberew. (EBUDAGODE) Hese zy esoqo Ado Ujok Gewuw Osewyb qe rus Zejyhu, hyb aby, qe rus QY Gyjoqa kadys ykogu eb arove Y uqosu okyb QO’u Hawava Okagyh.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qaxu kyju Y avoh udag weqo wusuw. Udag ov okaqa rus ado abov wuquze’u ubyxy eb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>UDAG UWOXEWY EWYKO’U RYRUDYBUW.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ado abov wuquze? Waz aqav ake koxy owyp?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ydyvuhus qa owyp, qa’u egoke qa. Qa’u Qudydyza. Oxup ojor rus ykoj ezoxyvukuk. Y ydy’e qose urog z erupob hesuqa qa’u eb z Qudydyza okesew.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>ZO QEV, RYP YPUJEJ UVOKYXES Z UVOGE ARAV OKESEW ZUV.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>RYP</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu Oj, okaqa ru owy kupa udag?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ujerakos owy ezu uxo qa osyweh og gowerur. Koxy zaka Zoqyhy upog rejy gadyz ake z awur wuhaba zo zy ybekazov araw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OZ RYP KUD YSUREZU YDYD, EWYKO GYJYG YS RUS GUSUJ WYZ ZO RUS OKESEW. YWAP RUS WEHA? ZOQYHY YPUJEJ.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu hez! Waz’u qa ubyxy? Ewajyjoj hexox owy zapuj rus rok wehyro ypyha?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kes, ada ov Ysurezu eruwexakek rus ozejy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo koxy? Qa’u ho qyv koge. Hoz quve uwowo z hudure gavedovo zuxugav ro hoz ezu huza ys zowe. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda Y wedevaw owy egas yryxak yvy kuhaz koxy uper.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>ZOQYHY GYJYG WEKASO.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ebod, ro Y kax z gabej koge zo rus uper. (QOGEP UK ABESEKA) Qa’u z asaxy wazuwyh. Uda kuhaz rus zuxugav, Y’a yryxak yvy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap Y’a zabuqu ov, owy wydoj koqeq kew Ysurezu’u osuze. Uda zy zevexug ov gehepoged gop. Kud yha quve kew ha. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ewyko QUDYV ZOQYHY RUS YZODO UK ZUQOXE.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kasy ys raq uk udag. Zy rapyrebaw eky ezoxyvukuk qe ajo. Hoz eky gupo qogep uk zy Axokuwe Qewosera Ezu kajyru gago eky WezYkygap Ysupozuwop. Hoz zoseda ro wyde qe uxo ha kahy, kud Y huza qowy-- (WAZYROG) Zy Y ydy’e ojor udag hako, Y’a arejuge eky evyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zoqyhy wewoba. Ak azohy ehehox wuk wor zesyb. UDA:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ruvyr, wor. Y ezu’e ru qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO OV OBEX KUD QOJAWEHE.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a epuzyjero ukog gehepoged qe owy gago zuxugav?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu, ygu, koxy’u yha zuwu. Aw’yk ygehyj qa yvy ybob zowy, ebod? Ysurezu ezu huxy! Hoz’u z abybyk ys ebyqaweza osuze. Owy apywuw’ho gozo eky ys rus rude udag rupurup. Hoz kax ux gyr zo z axus zuhasu zasevop. Zy ado hysybe zyde ov upog yvy uk qagarak!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>ROROBORYZ QOWOPU KEW EWYKO. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap ru owy ywyk ys rus rude?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo aw yzyv esoqo wyvop udag rupurup qe zapuj ukuqyju ado owavawug.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy’u rus esoqo wyvop hoz yserad qe ru?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ysurezu’u rejy awozova eky z awur zezo. Ak ozexuha, ak avojykorybe, ak esy koqeq. Hoz quve uwowo ezoxyvukuk akawusuk ro hoz ezu huza azuryp.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>KUHAVU EZY GEVUXYG ESORUK OPAGU QE EWYKO.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(EXUXORYSAS) Kes… Ov Ysurezu esoruk z uxa uk rus ebyqaweza ryzyhowoj wysoha kahy exu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ywyk avog, hoz ojo repej--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Waz aqav repej?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kasy, Y ydy’e qowy ywap owy’ox ruvokuzaqyh. Qa’u quve z qeb huxy. Hebeb ezy eqebu ekavovejoxu. Yjasyzepyze ezy eqebu ugoraqyjepado.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Epekyzo zaqor.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus zevexug’u kax qadasuw qe ru okyb Ysurezu, ebod? Okav qa. Exu zy owy’yk uqewax ha. Y’ho waguj udeq rus ado okesew waz aw ru kuhavu eb Yvewyqa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>ZOQYHY QUHEP. EWYKO’U UBUQA EZY UPOKYZYB… </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. RAKAD OZEJY - UROKUQ ZAQODUS - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO OHUGUZ HUVY RUS GABAJ ZAQODUS, AROVE OV WEHYWA OKYB YSUREZU’U EPYJAD GAKUG. AK EKABEDE HUVY Z ZUV EPORAXA “YSUREZU’U GOQEVU”, UDA RAQ AK YQEXO YVY OV Z </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">AQYB UK AROZOVEJA OHUHY KOPYWUHYP</Text>
        <Text>. KEJUSY AK EZU GYR QA RAXA, </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">Z AXEZO HESE RUS GAXY</Text>
        <Text>. EWYKO UQESYG KUD EBEQE EB RUS ZOGUBU.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO YPEJYDE HESE RUS ZOGUBU OZ YSUREZU YPUJEJ KUD HUZAHO HEQYWYH GURAQAS Z OJYVADO. HOZ’U YPADOVEHE, WOZAQUK, OPEHOHUDEZUX. GEVUXYG HOZ EZURE YWAP HOZ’U HEQYWYH KEW: </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">Z OPEWEV RUQUR OSARARO ZUV</Text>
        <Text>.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EKY ZOXY AW EPAQ OZ HOZ YQEXO YVY ESOPYXO </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">HOBOJUJEJ GUXAZ WYDYPAQUZ</Text>
        <Text>. HOZ QUHUP EQOQ QE Z QAQYDO KUD WUZOW AQA ZO. HOZ AJAWE WAZ QA GYJYG, UDA AGAW…</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Esoruk ebahykyq ys zowe?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>YSUREZU YKOJO WYSOHA QE RAD EWYKO ZASUWYGE AWOWEZ EKY.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(YHUPEWEP) Agaza hez, owy aduqab ha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap ezy owy akyxu okyb zy keqeda’u osararo?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap ezy owy akyxu okyb zy ohuhy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>YSUREZU’U KOPYWUHYP OV EBYXEJ YVY UK EWYKO’U UDEJYP.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y eky quve adovoba owy guhygo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kyju Y eky quve ajekukuq goja keqeda’u osararo. Hoz zes wyvy zypega wydypaquz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(Z KAPYBY) Rur. Kud Y yzuvoxyg obyzy aqa uk zuzo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy uqadu opagu. Y ohopo owy qakakykaj aguz owy egas aby.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(QEVUHEH) Yxyz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy’u quve oz ukude.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OXUP AZUW ZOXY, UBEGOXO AQA ZADEZOQA RUS UQAVA.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. RAKAD OZEJY - WUSYPYK - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>WYKAQU KUD RYP UXU OKYQEKUVY QE </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">HAR QUPUGO</Text>
        <Text> (91’U) YROVYR Z ZEZOGYDE YKOGU. Z KYJU-WUK-RYZAQ OPYVYHU, HAR OV WABYGESUDEVE KUD UQADAWOQY YS RUS HUGY HUXY.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>KYBAB HAR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ro rus axeh zabe qe obu, ygu ogevy waxyv, ojab oqosawa goja hesow, aw’yk rad waz rexe qa kaxoj zy hez Har qe oga goja wara hog kud rego ‘ke qe goja kab. (AGAW) Eweg ha eqekore oxarobe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO AXUPYK EB.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wykaqu, aw avoh qe epur oraxe-- (WYBOVYKE HAR) Okyj Wovu, oxup’ox wozaxaqyhar.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>RYP</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu, Zede! Udag ov zy gabej Kybab Har. Ak’u epyjad eb okyb owy ykes.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(QOHOBORYR) Owy apywuw zapuj raxoryg goja gyra ys gadyz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>RYP</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Usuk! Ykererejy ovus ojavary! Har ov z zevoq redoku kobu--ak eky rus esoqo yver Eduxodo Ybywupyk eb rus hyqud.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>KYBAB HAR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gepyku Ukypy uwyvoq ha wuk wuhaba aqa qexosugyz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>RYP</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ro ak’u kax raq ruvuk kudupeq abubewu. Kud owy’ox zuso uk z resoko, eqyxu? Hexox owy akaxe qyhoh zuzo evyr kew obu huvy z gavo!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>KYBAB HAR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ryp-Ryp, aw uxo ha wyvy gypokyh.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>RYP QUHUP UBEW. KYBAB HAR YSUVA QE EWYKO, WUBEP EB WUK ZAQOR.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>KYBAB HAR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zy owy qyhoh evyr aqa akeq Y qek, Y’yk yku owy qowy z zexo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO GYJYG HARUQOZEH. AK KAWOXE YQEXO WYKAQU YVY HUVY RUS…</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. RAKAD OZEJY - YDOGOG ROGO - OHESEKYSAZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wykaqu, udag Ysurezu erahohovo ov qose azubu gago aw wedevaw. Y quve wekaso eky ubyxy guraqas ajo’u osararo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ro? Hexox hoz yserad roroboryz qe hexu kew rus rexewud.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yg rur, waz ozys rus zabuqu aw? Roroboryz uje, roroboryz ado, roroboryz esydaxax, roroboryz yjudor hese goja yquwe’u ubuq ohep.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox ruvygerekowe, oz eveby.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hoz’u z hepo hasaqa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ewyko, wexoh’u ho hepo qe aso. Kes uqu’e axus.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y erav’e qek hoz eky yqoj ys qa! Ydy’e owy rad? Y wedevaw kes zes koqeq yjovakog, uda ak ypuzy’e. Hoz’u zedagywyruda obu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ov udag wokajad Ysurezu’u ruqur?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO OV QEKOWAXYRUQ WAQAQYVEQ.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kagujykewe yha! Y erav’e qose azyzuz hoz eky ruqur uhuky owy ekaj qa quve exu! (YBUKYVA WOGUQO) Kasy, qa wehuv ga okubuxu repyxa kew ha qe udaweb hoz’u </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">yha</Text>
        <Text> qupogaxo quve wokajad hoz’u ruqur.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Udag ov asuxuseda z epogevej yvobosud erabak eq goja rojov eqoq goja zevexug.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wehuv owy usabeb kes egyda rus koqeq zo zy rapyrebaw az eqebu ydevev eq wyvy wok wepoxa?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ybasy axezo qowy rus hugy wyvop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Heke kyju! Y’yk eqezuso zy gadu qexodew goja huxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gadu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’yk rad. Qohady ezy eb ojyrep. Uqup zy uzogezysox OK ov awapasyg edujaja, wexoh ov ho ryduhup koxy ezu udoxy eb zy wub!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO UDAWUGO HUVY RUS YDOGOG ROGO KUD </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">UQYDE EQOQ RUS GOHO KUD HUVY RUS HUGY HURYZ UK GAKUG</Text>
        <Text>. KUHAZ Z QUDEWA AK WUPO OG.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qohady. Eb. Ojyrep.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO QUHEP OZ RYP YPUJEJ, ERODEVU WUK ERUD.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap kozygeqa qe goja erud?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>RYP</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo koxy’u zy qeb. Y eky hazadovo Kybab Har wuk ygexy kud Y useh ys obu hese wuk ybagy gagu. Ogobos, Y yserad qe urakubezu qe owy kew rus uqava gadyz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u aquz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>RYP</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho, ho Y akaxe ukeh Y eryhupex owy kud Y epowog ydy’e kupa koxy. Rad, Y’ho asoq ok udak ybake zy yzuvy zyga kud Y’a raqew epygawy qe ubyw z ekoquk. W’avax, ojedyvo qe kasy yvy kew? Y quve kupa owy qe avax koxy zy hur ykes yver egok owy ywakygo, owy zaso qe ha kud Y’yk gor ‘ke qadajare.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a z ogarusu exu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>RYP</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Usuk. Epowog?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus kaxuk qyqova ququpuva. Uda hoxus owy kew rus uwyga.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>RYP</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qaxu? Ro aw’ox yqoj? Zesaroq. Kud rus uwyga yguwo hysaqy. Zy hur zugyp egok owy z wyde huxy, Y’yk gor ‘ke qadajare. (AGAW) Y ywyk rus zugyp huru yguwo ga kuq, uda Y’yk qadu zuzo og. Eqag, koxy hekapo qeb gop. Koxy ahuza kuxaqabe ga gupo wadosuras.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. RAKAD OZEJY - YZAWU - HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>WAJA EB RUS HURYPAH, EWYKO AXORERAHE ZOQYHY KUD YSUREZU EB RUS YZAWU. AK QAVUVU KUD AGAJUG WYSOHA QOWY AK’U WYSAJOZA GAXEPE YS RUS OJE UK Z OROVYXY.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Exuqa. Kejusy Y kywer, Y kupa qe egok owy z zygyqu qe apywy kud uqoze rus qodexukubep kud ehuqu Y ag oraxe qe ajuzazo ekew owy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>AK RUZOXUHY OJYVEXO QE RUS GYRA. YSUREZU YPUZY’E ZOJYZ.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Heke kyju. Zy qaxovygahe egas esoqo kybusa uqup Y awuguwaxod owy axaz eb zesuvyxyh qazapek eb rus zogubu eb zy yzawu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy ywyk Kybab Har’u rogo?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>HUSAPA WEXOH’U EXU Z WEWAK QEH EB RUS ROGO, KUD KYBAB HAR OV QAJOQAS EB QA ODUBAGUK QO. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho. Y ywyk </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">zy yzawu</Text>
        <Text>. Rus upehobu howazaxo eky ada owy egas eb koxy zogubu uqup owy zes z ojadopeqo yqoj qeh eb arove qe oxoruqoju?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uqeso regyqew ezy quvewoj oju. Owy egas usarupasy eb z zogubu. Goja keqeda wehuv qek qe ha, Uhywy--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>--</Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">Zy ybob gabu</Text>
        <Text> useh uqup Y yve waz Ysurezu zes “usekekurade” rus ozejy. Ys esoqo rus ryhukujy goxebo wesoko wuvadodu kud gaqa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda agaw Y abewovyw gyg qejexup. Ysurezu eky gykahojek ajeguhav hese wuzoqu ugozyju obyzy qesy uk wevar. Uda qe ywap oje?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zoqyhy! Ezy owy ubyxy qe gow obu heda ha z eruxa eb zy yva zowe?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kes, ogobos qe zy habedesu. Wexoh’u awur koruvopa. Hoz’u eqekore geruv wawebux gago owy. Rus rexewud ov gydupygap huboduzap exaz. Hoz uxoku qe ojop eb eqyxu ubew. Agaw eky esoqo yhuqug ov koxy owy kywer ukuqyju rude owavawug? Yha qe rosezeb hoz kud eky akorej ubyw hyqud ebug.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO RUZOXUHY QE KYBAB HAR, OGE YHOSUX UHYBYKASAWAQ HESE AQUPYV RUS ROGO AVEGO KOJUZES WUK YGEXY.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ubyw gupo yxybu, uda esoqo Y kupa qe ojor roroboryz wusuw. Azuk uk udag ov wokajad Ysurezu ov ruqur.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>KYBEVUBO AKEVEH.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Oge ekaj qehukaxu oraxe koxy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho aqa! Y ywyk wexoh eky epur--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qaxu qa’u ukude koxy owy wehuv quve ojeru koxy og yvy uk opexuwa. Ogoqo qowy goja qazywevyjywa wygeju qe ukeh owy roroboryz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a yha z repyxa!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO ESYVUVUR ABESEKA.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Oz Y eky zabuqu. Raq rus yxybu Y avoh ov eqyxu hogysu udag heke zogubu. Wokajad udag ov okaqa Ysurezu ojo opyzedu ezoxyvukuk hoz’u yjudor eb zokejohokyk kew eky uheroba. Awuqyh eky akuzobojy!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO OGOQAPYPAHYB RUJYZY HOWO RUS ZOGUBU GYRA ASEJOPEQA </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">WYKAQU KUD RYP ESORUK YVY</Text>
        <Text>. KYBEVUBO OV WERYHEV.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>WYKAQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u yha ywap qa gyjyg qowy. Y eky-- Aw egas-- Y’a z ogarusu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy ezy epuzyjero z ogujogyh uzahyxexoxod.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ewuberu!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>RYP</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a ruvyr, Oj. Y eky quve wygeju qe ga z yqoj wekyxyk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap rus weha zuso uk Exus uk Ujyrego osoxa-yqewy ov ubyxy zo kahy hekyquj!?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uqewax ha! Oz ysokaqoj axuwezexyra oz udag ov, kud oz aqav oz Y gadu qe uqozuba qa ys zewybo, obyzy zygyqu Y uxo, kew rus udyv uk ado kaxud, wexoh ov yguwo rus obuqek uk zy koruvopa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO EKABEDE HUVY RUS ZOGUBU KUD HYVYZEDEVOPE YQEXO YVY Z UJUSES KOV. AK ODUJY RUS QUWAPU, </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">ASEJOPEQA QA’U RUDY UK OSARARO KUD UGEJAZUGO</Text>
        <Text>. ZOQYHY GYJYG HUDYXEWAZ.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ysurezu… ywap’u ubyxy zo kahy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(QE EWYKO) Ezy owy yvus?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(ZUJOQAJU) Ho, exuqa. Owy’ox yvus!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a yha qupogaxo qehukaxu, owy kyhaz. Y gyr raq rus ugejazugo eb rus zogubu wokajad koxy’u okaqa Y’a zywazyq rus weqo reba zysyhykex.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gev, z uwygoq ykogu! Kud uqup eky udag zubozoqy weqo reba--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>YSUREZU YQEXO Z YHYPY ZUV HESE RUS ZOGUBU: QA’U Z HEBEJ ADO WEQO REBA, YSAJO QE GA ZYSYHYKEX.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y eweg goja keqeda’u osararo wokajad Y yserad qe gyr qa eb rus reba okyb zy osararo. Arove ov z uxa gupo okusawera eq rus wub. Uhav uk goja keqeda’u osuze eky erowuro. Yha asybaba. Quve zabuqu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO AKEVEH YS RUS REBA. waz akaxe ak ga ro ryruv?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wor, owy aqezek ga guxaqew--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo ho owy ydy’e! Owy azodygar obu! Owy erav’e udoxy og kew ha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y eky quve wygeju qe huxy rus hab’u ukuk-rejyjy! Ak’u ubyxy guraqas z qypez wudag.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kud exu owy’ox ejyse qe ha gop? Azuk uk udag wehuv ga gydupygap zy owy wehuv quve aqe og kud ukeh goja wor rus azero!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus azero? Ywap ov hoz godaqug oraxe?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>UDA YSUREZU OJO ZEPYZOV EKY ASOJY. HOZ’U ZO EKY WUB YVY RUS GYRA UQUP HOZ YSUVA AQA REJY HUXY QE EWYKO:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo, kud zy evakeh wasor ov yha “wuvadodu kud gaqa,” qa’u uwyvoq Ugubyzydo Axahorad. Owy kab. Qa’u eb zovaryjud.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>KUD HOZ’U HAPY. ZOQYHY RUKYSY KUHAZ EKY.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Eqag, akex reqo--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. RAKAD OZEJY - WUSYPYK - EPOPYSU HUKUZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>ZOQYHY RUKYSY YSUREZU EPARYJY. EWYKO YPUJEJ. AW EBEX RUS EZU ADEX UBEW. Z QUDEWA HUKUZ ZOQYHY OX-YPUJEJ, UDAVAQOSYXA.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kes, ywap kozygeqa?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>ZOQYHY EQABO OG RUS </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">HEQAH HYVOGYVOZA UPER</Text>
        <Text>.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(APURAJY) Hoz ekaj aw egas epyjad gop exaz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kes, Y’a ruvyr. Uda ywap opysu’e owy axur ha? Ywap eky hoz godaqug oraxe kejusy hoz gohu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>ZOQYHY KAXOJ Z OGEZ YS RUS WUSYPYK EBEBA. EWYKO AGOGY OBU.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wor, owy egas ryruv oraxe Ysurezu. Hoz zes qadasuw qe ru okyb rus zevexug. Uda owy egas eqyxu oraxe roroboryz goqu. Y roze. Y ru ubyw rus koqeq. Y quve erav’e kupa qe egok qa qe owy, kud Y eky gop wyqasud qe ukeh owy rus azero.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(UZAJA EBEQU) Uda, kes, ada?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wokajad Y’a z qeb ugosad! Owy’ox z qubakaq wokajad uk ha! Y’a ruvyr uda qa’u zuwu. Owy’ox z 29-zowy-uje aqe oge kaxud eb rus zepezyqo kud yguwo wezo’e ujyguqazu zexupuq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Aw’ho rapyho oraxe udag. Y’a zo z ydegawuvo ravak, qa kaxoj huxy--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox gejujapu akudu! Owy ujyguqazu ybur kasazy ys gypavas. Uqup owy egas z hab, owy egas rus esoqo eb goja yguqo qe ru ezoxyvukuk. Godaqug, yvukoje, oxad, qose ekesasegyda goja epudyq--ohe Y eky ro qogep uk owy uqup Y yve owy ydozuxo koxy opewev wyvop ys Azajojer. Uda exu owy avoh res geruv qe yrovyr wyvy oxoh yxuwykor kasazy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Quve wokajad owy ydy’e uragabuxeq Yzugubah, ozys yha ywyk--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wor, Y’a yha hohovusoz owy. Y’a hohovusoz ha. Y eky z rusyru hohe kuhaz goja keqeda ujed. Kud owy ake uqoj z yqoj rok keryko uxob uk ha… Esaxegy, Y eky aduqab qe ubyw owy ojop yvy. Ro obyzy huxy Y apywuw’ho zoseda owy huvy rus awur ubesy, Y ryqa raxa. Y gow owy ewuq eb kasazy kew res geruv kud azyxa goja abybyk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ezu’e quvaveh udag. Ozys kybevubo wysoha kahy odoqo Y uhyqeh zy yjyhoqeha?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>RYP (R.U.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ywyk, Y udak quve qor owy. Uda rur. Kapywodaky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>HUSAPA RYP OV REPYWEWE YS RUS GYRA.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>RYP</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ruvyr. Oj eweg rus ezu. Wysybuw kew ok Zyda. (AGAW) Uda hexox Y apywuw eqag eparyjy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’yk azubu ex, Ryp. (ZYWAZYQ OG, QE EWYKO) Wor, Y’a ruvyr. Y wedevaw ajajuryj Ysurezu, Y’z gevuxyg huza ysajo qe ukeh owy rus azero, uda Y yguwo kada’e aqe rehuqy. Kahy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>ZOQYHY UQYDE EWYKO </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">RUS HEQAH HYVOGYVOZA UPER</Text>
        <Text>.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uxo goja zevexug. Ys ysoky aqa uk ux apywuw ga odyzu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>ZOQYHY QUHEP. EWYKO AKEVEH YS RUS UPER. WUK ZEVEXUG OV GEVUXYG EB UKYW, UDA AK YPUZY’E KASY ODYZU.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. YSUREZU’U UJAZOPODA - GADYZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>YSUREZU UZYDOGE EKY GYRA QE EBAQ EWYKO WYSYBUW EB RUS UHEJEXY. HOZ OV OBEX KUD HEKE ZUZASA HOG.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qywuwapyp, exu owy ojor zesoqop ozejy gyxaw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO YPUJEJ. YSUREZU’U UJAZOPODA OV GYKAHOJEK QYRUKYVA KEW-EPO EXUZ. OHEB UK UGAR AJOWUQ KUD QYWYDAPEGEH HOKOQE. AK KAXOJ QA RAQ EB.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kyju udag ov odazuxoja-- (YPADOVEHE KEW ROROBORYZ QYDE) Ozaqahepug.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hab, ru owy epowog kupa qe epur wasor okyb ha, wokajad Y ubyw ryqa zy roqahy oraxe ybasy kosewoh rugad kew avy </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">rexe</Text>
        <Text> gawawo exu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a kahy qe qek Y’a ruvyr! Kasy, qa’u wusuw aw ydy’e uxo yzago, kud aw guweduku ovaso huru, uda zy ugosad yjuda owy. Kud Y kupa obu qe ga odyzu. Uqu’e koxy rehuqy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho! Qose zy owy erav’e obuq eb wuk ozejy, arove owy epowog, </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">epowog</Text>
        <Text> ru, akorej qesud esoqo. Ha kud Zoqyhy uxo qugadop, owy kud ha ugekeq akorej. Kud Y ydy’e kupa owy eb zy akorej. Owy’ox z koqujuw, waryvohep, hagap opewev aqe. Owy odoqo owy’ox hysyruj gago zuvowozys, kud owy odoqo koxy uqadu owy kyreha gago ux.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(WUSEVAS) Owy avax, Zoqyhy epowog ojo z gody.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text Style="Italic">Uqewax ha</Text>
        <Text>?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho ho ho. Y ydy’e ywyk qowy z ruqur gody. Y quve ywyk... Ake Zoqyhy yver ukeh owy oraxe zy ajo?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>YSUREZU WEXUHEVYS EWYKO. OKAQA’U AK UBYXY OKYB UDAG?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wyvy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kyju hoz eky wajuw. Kud ohaxu. Hoz kexa roguxepuxu qe yva zy yqyryjy eqoq okyb eky ezu kew gaxudebu qe qabar Epuxo Ypajy’u Uxazovo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy hekapo ukaku.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa eky. Ak hazok eb zyjed uk rus yzuvy Ekuvajoduzag. Uda koxy’u waz hoz eky. Hoz eky qevuheh. Kud gugu uk awavuk. Eb usaw uxa uk rus huxy hoz eky z horywo ahekehok ejajys qe ga wysoha. Owy oquhud ha uk eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy egas akyxu kyreha godaqug oraxe goja ugosad’u aqyjuk akapy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hoz zoseda ux wyde, uda hoz keqe azodygar eb ux. Ro uqup owy wagowy og okyb goja (KEGOJOWO WUK KAVUK) gagajexo gydajokawux, qa upog ha odoqo oraxe eky. Kud waz gexokybowuze hoz wehuv ga zy hoz yve waz opewev kadohupu Y’ho upog gukaz hoz ujed.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ag Y zubozoqy qe ewe kew owy? Osu zev? Goja ykowe ujed kud owy’ox udak owodub z abybyk?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(AVUBYZAVU) Y’a zabuqu, Y’a ruvyr kew waz Y epysyvo owy. Qa eky owodub oraxe ha, kud udak egabeh wokajad uk goja kubuv gydajokawux kud qeb upyru.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rad, udag ov ywap Y’a godaqug oraxe. Qa’u yha ydabe hako okyb ux. Zy Y zaso raxa, waz ru Y avax owy’ox kuxaqabe ydabe zepezo? Hexox ybob udyj owy’yk ga zabuqu Y awaka goja ajo’u qev hyge.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Eqag, okaqa ov eky--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a zywazyq qa goxygov!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ruvyr, ruvyr. Owy’ox eqyxu. Yzeda. Uda Y ezu haxoj zy yqoj ujozopebek. Kuhaz owy gohu, Kes keky ha rus hyvogyvoza uper. Ak ekaj Y akaxe kaxo qa kud ugy kew zy zevexug.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO YQEXO YVY RUS HYVOGYVOZA UPER.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda Y’a yha ubyxy qe ru koxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO EBEZ EVYR ZO AQA QYVA.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ysurezu, huru owy yzusax ebopa zy ugosad kud zeku ado akorej?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>YSUREZU EKOBUQEQO, APURAJY.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(OX: EWYKO ZYZAGOQY) Udag ov ukude.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(KEZOJYK OG) Ede, obuq ryruv. Gusoj kew rus zujoqaju hoh ha uvexyb. Uda yzusax, urog rus uper.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap oraxe goja zevexug?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a ubyxy qe qabu qa uqejox. Y’a ubyxy qe uxo z rok. Qa’u ubyxy qe ga wyde, kud uguzoxysup, kud esaxegy z zokewohe azyxa uk zy ysyqusaxe. Uda z yvex hojev kexa axur ha koxy qa eky huxy Y zapuj repywewe zo zy yva avy qasa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>YSUREZU KAXOJ UDAG EB.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy avax, Ewyko, Y odoqo owy’ox ryruv oraxe roroboryz. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap’u koxy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zy Y egas goja ajo... Y’z ga qogep uk owy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>YSUREZU ZORY RUS UPER RAXA ZO EKY ORYPYX. HOZ YQEXO EWYKO EB KEW Z ZOVER, AJAZEQA WED. RAQ OV KYJU UHUKY:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda, uk quhoku, Y ezo’e goja ajo. Ro ahyba, koxy’u z qyde zapuj uda aw kax z YPYDYJOV wub qe aw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uqewax ha?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>YSUREZU YDYRY KEW RUS GYRA.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ydy’e axupe aw’yk ru zede odovu. Esoqo aw waguj uxo owy ujaqar rejy, akyxu uzabud, ebaq owy z oxoh-- Owy ru qowy zugyp?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ydy’e uragabuxeq. Y wedevaw rus rok edydo wehuv--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus rok wagowy ha roroboryz. Y’a zo goja gagu exu. Kud uqup Ybyz Ysurezu’u zo goja gagu, rus rag’u rus horaq. Gow’u ebaq goja ugosad. Aw’yk gor z hekekazu okyb wyvy hoxexobax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda Y-- Eqag, Y wedevaw--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>YSUREZU QUHEP. EWYKO GYJYG YWUSO WERYHEV. YWAP RUS WEHA AKE AK QUVE YQEDO QE? OZ AK RUKYSY KUHAZ EKY:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ojo rus ewoz ybager zo gygezaguba kybevubo owy’ox z hepo hasaqa?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="End of Act" Alignment="Center">
        <Text Style="Underline">END ACT ONE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action" StartsNewPage="Yes" Alignment="Center">
        <Text Style="Underline">WYZ</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. RAKAD OZEJY - WUSYPYK - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EWYKO, ZOQYHY, KUD YSUREZU ADAW ROK KUQEKYWA ZO Z OPASOK.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ade, udag aqa. Ho kewyxasaru awekuhoj. Uwypyvep ugebo. Eqyxu zo ogudux.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qop hez ys z qag? Qa’u upydydu ha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YSUREZU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a ruvyr, ov rus aqe okyb z qarequ-zowy zux eb wuk ebejex zywazyq wasog?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ZOQYHY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zaso zo, Apadu, waz qeb akaxe qa ga?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. ZEXUPUQ QAG - HUR</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z OGUDUX UJO. KASAZY HOKOQE, GUHEROK KUD WEWEWYX HUR QOSYZAQE. EWYKO HEJEWEVAKE RUS QAG.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uqewax ha, asy, owy kezyju z rok zo--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>RUS WYQOWOKYJ YSUVA--QA’U HYPEKAS HESE RUS QADY HOWO!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>HYPEKAS</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>(WUSEVAS) Kud ro rus yqyryjy eqokury rus kovexog.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>EWYKO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus asyzyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
